### 获取当前用户附件列表
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/GetMyAttachments?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取当前用户附件列表（按业务类型过滤）
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/GetMyAttachments?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&businessType=Avatar
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

### 获取当前用户附件列表（按关键字过滤）
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Attachment/GetMyAttachments?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&keyword=avatar
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}

